last_episode_to_air.name: A New Day
last_episode_to_air.overview: It’s a new day with new surprises for Fiona — and not all of them are good. New drama unfolds between her, Jane, and AJ and in the fallout, Fiona finds herself stuck in an entirely new situation.

name: Stuck
overview: Fiona is stuck reliving the same day over and over again and must find a way to break the curse.

episodes.overview: Fiona decides to make it a good day by being kind to everyone in her life. She quickly discovers that her positive actions have positive consequences — including one very special moment with AJ at the school dance that could change her life forever.
